 shouldn't be"],[6158,6333,"spending money he doesn't have."]],"35":[[175,312,"You stupid bitch!"],[366,470,"You'll never know what it's like"],[470,620,"to carry a man's child,"],[654,920,"or just how far he'll go for you."],[954,1025,"You'll never know."],[1070,1141,"Wait,"],[1175,1350,"so, she's broke"],[1350,1441,"and barren?"],[1520,1620,"Jesus."],[1620,1762,"That's so tragic."],[1791,1900,"What's tragic"],[1900,2058,"is that none of you have changed."],[2091,2229,"You're still the same"],[2229,2350,"shallow,"],[2350,2625,"narcissistic assholes from high school."],[2625,2729,"That is it."],[2729,2850,"Take off that fake dress now,"],[2850,2958,"you little tramp."],[3004,3166,"Or we'll do it for you."],[3220,3291,"Fred?"],[3358,3425,"Get her."],[3975,4045,"Whoa!"],[4079,4354,"Three cheers for Bailey broke-ass."]],"36":[[129,425,"Three cheers for Bailey Brokeass."],[2062,2154,"You know what?"],[2179,2237,"I don't think"],[2237,2416,"you deserve a dress that beautiful."],[2450,2637,"Give me that fake-ass necklace."],[2954,3075,"Come and get it, bitch."],[3300,3450,"Fred, the shoes."],[3579,3725,"Cheap-ass knock-offs."],[4516,4679,"Get your hands off my wife."]],"37":[[658,737,"You okay?"],[879,995,"Give me a fucking break."],[995,1162,"Your little wife deserved it."],[1183,1262,"Mason."],[1308,1375,"Just go."],[1383,1520,"Look, they assaulted you."],[1562,1691,"I'm not letting that go."],[1791,1962,"You'll all be hearing from my lawyers."],[1979,2141,"Oh, I'm shaking with fear."],[2141,2220,"You should be."],[2220,2270,"Why?"],[2270,2375,"You can't do anything."],[2375,2504,"You're a fucking nobody."],[2520,2658,"Didn't you say he was a construction"],[2658,2800,"worker at Apex?"],[2804,2929,"I'm Fred Lauren,"],[2966,3125,"Apex Senior Marketing Director."],[3141,3279,"One call and you lose your job."],[3279,3487,"So, watch how you talk to us, hotshot."],[3604,3716,"How's the reunion going?"],[3766,3920,"I'm gonna need you to come down here"],[3920,4037,"and bring termination"],[4037,4183,"paperwork for a douche named"],[4183,4283,"Fred Lauren."],[4300,4404,"This will be fun."],[4433,4529,"See you soon."],[4758,4845,"What the hell was that?"],[4866,4983,"I just fired your ass."]],"38":[[175,279,"You hear this guy?"],[279,437,"A construction worker thinks"],[437,566,"he can talk to me like this."],[612,775,"You're just a low-life thug"],[775,916,"pretending to be some big shot."],[1016,1150,"You're so screwed, Bailey."],[1150,1291,"I hope you like being homeless,"],[1291,1379,"because that's how you"],[1379,1466,"and your little family"],[1466,1575,"are gonna end up"],[1575,1741,"when Fred's through with you."],[1800,2016,"We can't let anything happen to Hannah."],[2016,2075,"Look, I'm not gonna"],[2075,2254,"let anything happen to our family."],[2316,2391,"Trust me?"],[2587,2679,"You're a fool."],[2700,2912,"I'm calling the VP of Apex right now."],[2954,3154,"Roger Sanders is a close friend."],[3175,3362,"You're done at Apex."],[3366,3454,"I'm gonna have Roger"],[3454,3579,"make an example out of you."],[3600,3754,"You won't get a job laying bricks"],[3754,3850,"when I'm through with you."],[3929,4016,"That's funny."],[4016,4166,"He's who I just called."],[4166,4300,"Here, why don't you call him back?"],[4466,4641,"Enough of this charade!"],[4641,4679,"You don't have"],[4679,4854,"Roger Sanders' number, asshole."],[4854,4954,"You've never met him."],[4954,5141,"You're just a blue-collar nobody."],[5183,5312,"I'm proud of my husband."],[5433,5566,"He makes an honest living."],[5708,5812,"Honest?"],[6012,6141,"That's rich."],[6366,6516,"Yes, Mason."],[6566,6862,"Why don't you tell your new wifey poo"],[6891,7058,"how you have the Apex VP"],[7058,7179,"on speed dial?"]],"39":[[16,145,"What are you doing here, Clarice?"],[145,358,"Oh, I'm here with Chad."],[391,541,"He was captain of the football team."],[541,666,"Don't play dumb."],[683,825,"Dude, don't talk about my woman"],[825,895,"like that."],[895,1008,"Stay out of this, Brad."],[1054,1170,"It's Chad."],[1358,1641,"You are so selfish."],[1745,1879,"Did you even think"],[1916,2033,"what people would say"],[2033,2116,"when they found out"],[2116,2383,"you replaced me with a janitor?"],[2383,2508,"So are you stalking me now?"],[2637,2866,"Please, don't flatter yourself."],[2941,3045,"I'm more interested"],[3045,3183,"in getting to know her."],[3216,3358,"What does this homewrecker have"],[3358,3454,"that I don't?"],[3454,3545,"Wait, wait, wait."],[3545,3645,"Homewrecker?"],[3733,3970,"So Bailey Brokeass turned out to be"],[3970,4145,"the biggest loser,"],[4145,4470,"but also the biggest slut in our class."],[4579,4658,"Figures."],[4658,4783,"Since she's sterile,"],[4783,5033,"I bet she lets guys fuck her bareback."],[5195,5333,"No wonder you're trying to"],[5333,5495,"steal my daughter."],[5533,5629,"Because you can't even"],[5629,5754,"have a child of your own."],[5754,5883,"Okay, that is enough, Clarice."],[5920,6054,"I don't think it is."],[6408,6645,"This is really a hazard."],[6708,7004,"Somebody could fall and get really hurt."],[7158,7441,"Why don't you be a good little janitor?"],[7533,7616,"Clean it up."]],"40":[[600,675,"Clean it up!"],[833,962,"Back off."],[1137,1287,"Careful, Mason."],[1350,1500,"You wouldn't want your new wife"],[1500,1575,"to find out"],[1575,1758,"what you really do for a living."],[1908,2020,"I know what he does."],[2095,2233,"He shows up."],[2287,2387,"He provides."],[2408,2675,"He's honest and loving"],[2775,2895,"and trustworthy."],[2983,3250,"And he's an amazing dad and husband."],[3287,3408,"He's more than I could ask for."],[3720,3808,"Are you done?"],[3870,3975,"That's cute."],[4050,4358,"Now shut up and clean the floor."],[4520,4645,"Bailey, Bailey, don't."],[4645,4862,"Go on, Miss Cain."],[4895,4958,"Show us all"],[4958,5183,"what you're really made of."]],"41":[[70,212,"It's okay, Mason."],[337,512,"I'm not embarrassed that I'm a janitor."],[670,858,"This job led me to you and Hannah."],[900,995,"If mopping the floor"],[995,1150,"proves my love for my family,"],[1287,1583,"then I'll do it a thousand times over."],[1595,1675,"You know what?"],[1700,1800,"I changed my mind."],[1870,1970,"Scrub the floor"],[2008,2137,"on your knees."],[2208,2337,"Where you really belong."],[2583,2733,"Okay, you just crossed the line."],[2787,2925,"If I crossed another,"],[2995,3137,"what if I told her"],[3137,3408,"about the billions of lies"],[3408,3525,"you've been keeping from her?"],[3525,3675,"Don't test me, Clarice."],[3908,4275,"I am going to get the best lawyers"],[4275,4537,"so that you never see Hannah again."],[4850,4995,"What the hell is going on here?"]],"42":[[137,270,"What the hell is going on here?"],[454,558,"It's about time."],[900,1037,"I'm sorry about Clarice."],[1070,1125,"It's okay."],[1212,1370,"Roger, thank God."],[1395,1558,"I need to fire this construction worker."],[1558,1700,"He's completely out of line."],[1837,2062,"Fred Lauren, I hereby terminate you"],[2062,2175,"from the Apex group."],[2233,2462,"And you will be given no severance."],[2462,2520,"What?"],[2570,2675,"What are you talking about?"],[2712,2850,"You can't do this."],[2850,2925,"Oh, I can."],[2925,3100,"Roger, your phone please."],[3208,3325,"I'm calling the police"],[3345,3450,"to report a violation"],[3450,3550,"of our restraining order."],[3575,3687,"Did you forget you're not supposed"],[3687,3833,"to be within 300 feet of me?"],[4012,4125,"This isn't over."],[4270,4500,"I know where you work, bitch."],[4550,4762,"And I'm gonna get my Hannah back,"],[4795,4908,"one way or the other."]],"43":[[37,270,"And I'm gonna get my Hannah back,"],[300,420,"one way or the other."],[812,883,"Mason,"],[987,1050,"what do we do?"],[1625,1700,"We're going home."],[1825,1962,"Take out the trash for me, would you?"],[1975,2070,"Way ahead of you."],[2537,2595,"Roger."],[2625,2745,"Please, help me fix this."],[2745,2850,"I'll do anything."],[2850,3008,"Oh, there's no help anymore."],[3025,3200,"Once the CEO is done with you,"],[3245,3329,"it's over."],[3395,3487,"CEO?"],[3520,3600,"That guy?"],[3787,3962,"Oh my God."],[4037,4120,"What have we done?"]],"44":[[783,833,"Hannah?"],[845,1108,"Is staying over at Mrs. Flannigan's."],[1208,1304,"So, we're-"],[1304,1379,"All alone."],[1645,1720,"Bailey, there's something"],[1720,1833,"that I need to tell you."],[1920,2304,"But first, I've been dying to do this"],[2304,2370,"all night."],[3120,3175,"More."],[3608,3708,"Bailey, we gotta,"],[3708,3795,"we gotta talk."],[3833,3883,"There are things"],[3883,4033,"that you don't know about me."],[4120,4233,"I know that you're a good man."],[4295,4408,"And that I feel safe with you."],[4520,4620,"That's all that matters."]],"45":[[362,425,"Look."],[516,687,"I don't want you to feel like you have to."],[812,925,"You make me feel at home."],[1041,1154,"I've never felt that before."],[1279,1412,"Let me be that place for you."],[1454,1529,"Every day."],[3966,4204,"God, you are so beautiful, Bailey."],[4329,4466,"I can't believe I found you."],[4566,4650,"I'm yours."],[4712,4854,"Every part of me."]],"46":[[650,712,"Danny!"],[762,862,"Where the hell have you been?"],[1333,1487,"Give me that bracelet."],[1487,1558,"Fuck, no!"],[1558,1650,"Are you out of your mind?"],[1650,1750,"You shut up!"],[1895,2012,"If I don't pay,"],[2050,2195,"they're gonna bury me, okay?"],[2195,2287,"These loan sharks."],[2312,2470,"Then ask your precious sister."],[2800,2891,"Maybe, I will."],[3058,3187,"One night with Mr. Pitt."],[3362,3537,"That's 30k right there."],[3675,3770,"I just gotta get rid of"],[3770,3933,"that construction dickwad."]],"47":[[458,654,"And here comes Hannah Cain"],[670,833,"with the flip of the century."],[854,1083,"But will she stick the landing?"],[1454,1620,"Oh, she does!"],[1620,1795,"The crowd goes wild!"],[1820,1908,"I did it!"],[1916,2033,"I did it, Daddy!"],[2083,2170,"Morning, Teach."],[2179,2258,"Morning, Coach."],[2320,2420,"Mommy!"],[2420,2658,"I missed you so much!"],[2670,2829,"I missed you more, sweetheart."],[2870,3066,"Daddy, don't just stand there."],[3066,3195,"Give Mommy a kiss."],[3683,3741,"Go on."],[4566,4695,"Fuel for your big day?"],[4733,4858,"You help make these, Hannah?"],[4908,4979,"Yep."],[4979,5141,"And they're better than the Chef's."],[5141,5254,"Right, Daddy?"]],"48":[[216,333,"What's this, Mommy?"],[366,458,"Lesson plans."],[491,654,"Today's my first day of teaching."],[691,945,"You're gonna be the best teacher ever."],[1058,1204,"I got you a power outfit."],[1204,1316,"I thought it would be perfect"],[1316,1395,"for your first day."],[1466,1604,"Is this MUSERA from SHEIN?"],[1604,1658,"Yeah."],[2408,2491,"I love it."],[2508,2633,"Thank you so much."],[2720,2833,"Knock them dead, Teach."],[2854,3108,"Knock them super dead, Mommy."],[4295,4379,"Hi, class."],[4433,4541,"I'm Miss Bailey,"],[4541,4733,"and I will be your first grade teacher"],[4745,4891,"while Mrs. White is away."],[5020,5395,"Hmm, I guess I'm Mrs. Cain now."],[5533,5720,"Okay, you've got this."]],"49":[[33,250,"No matter how much you rehearse,"],[287,512,"you'll still always sound like a janitor."],[600,837,"Clarice, what are you doing here?"],[862,1050,"You're not allowed near Hannah."],[1233,1425,"I just wanted to see my daughter"],[1462,1575,"one last time."],[1625,1758,"Save the performance."],[1812,1925,"You never cared for her."],[2012,2295,"Leave before I call security."],[2337,2425,"Call them."],[2775,2850,"Security?"],[2958,3120,"Clarice Cain is on the premise"],[3120,3270,"and she has a restraining order."],[3545,3625,"They're on the way."],[3750,3983,"Enjoy your shift, Miss Cain."],[4137,4300,"So you'll give Bailey the job?"],[4325,4545,"Lady, you give me another stack,"],[4612,4725,"I'll make her principal."],[5200,5325,"That's what you get for stealing"],[5325,5525,"someone else's billionaire husband."]],"50":[[479,604,"Morning, class."],[637,725,"I'm Miss Bailey"],[725,837,"and I will be your teacher"],[837,962,"while Mrs. White is away."],[962,1100,"Weren't you that lady"],[1100,1229,"who cleans our toilets?"],[1300,1537,"Uh, who can tell me"],[1537,1687,"who the first president was?"],[2004,2062,"What?"],[2154,2291,"What's happening to me?"],[2529,2629,"What's wrong with her?"],[2666,2750,"My daddy said"],[2750,2929,"a janitor can't be a teacher."],[2937,3004,"I think I'm..."],[3229,3354,"I think she's going to puke."],[3375,3454,"Yuck!"],[3454,3579,"Ew!"],[3579,3687,"Disgusting."],[3729,3837,"I'm so dizzy."],[4166,4316,"Bailey, what's going on in here?"]],"51":[[33,208,"Bailey, are you intoxicated?"],[300,387,"This is what I get"],[387,545,"for letting a lonely janitor think"],[545,612,"she's good enough"],[612,712,"to teach in my school."],[775,875,"God's sake."],[908,1012,"I bet a drunk like you"],[1012,1187,"doesn't even have a teaching license."],[1187,1325,"No, I do."],[1325,1450,"I want to be a teacher."],[1470,1558,"That's not happening."],[1558,1650,"Not at this school."],[1800,1950,"It just keeps getting better."],[3145,3333,"Bailey, are you intoxicated?"],[3475,3550,"This is what I get"],[3550,3708,"for letting a lonely janitor think"],[3708,3775,"she's good enough"],[3775,3858,"to teach in my school."],[3858,3983,"Do you really think"],[3983,4137,"this person is suitable"],[4137,4279,"to be a mother for Hannah?"]],"52":[[1312,1379,"What happened?"],[1479,1591,"I messed it all up."],[1829,1879,"I don't know."],[1879,1987,"It was all a blur."],[2129,2266,"Mason, what am I gonna do?"],[2341,2416,"I've wanted this"],[2416,2579,"for as long as I can remember."],[2641,2766,"And I screwed it up."],[2854,2979,"No one's gonna trust me"],[2979,3066,"with their kids again."],[3250,3366,"Hey, hey."],[3629,3712,"I trust you."],[4366,4512,"Now can you tell me anything"],[4512,4591,"that you did differently"],[4591,4675,"this morning?"],[4766,4900,"Did you eat anything funny?"],[4941,5079,"I just had some coffee."]],"53":[[25,158,"Now can you tell me anything"],[158,250,"that you did differently"],[250,333,"this morning?"],[433,550,"Did you eat anything funny?"],[600,737,"I just had some coffee."],[1070,1133,"Security?"],[1237,1408,"Clarice Cain is on the premise"],[1408,1562,"and she has a restraining order."],[1825,1987,"I saw Clarice."],[2062,2162,"You don't think..."],[2550,2700,"Just stay right here, okay?"],[4020,4195,"How many times do I have to say it?"],[4212,4350,"Stay the fuck away"],[4350,4462,"from me and my wife."]],"54":[[41,162,"I heard your wife"],[162,316,"had an embarrassing first day"],[316,412,"as a teacher."],[516,725,"How long has she been off the wagon?"],[750,837,"Did you really think that"],[837,916,"I wouldn't find out"],[916,1025,"that you were behind this?"],[1041,1129,"Doesn't matter."],[1179,1325,"I got the video footage"],[1325,1516,"that I need to show my lawyers"],[1554,1716,"that Bailey is not fit"],[1729,1850,"to be around Hannah"],[1866,2166,"or around any kids, actually."],[2166,2316,"What happens when I tell the judge"],[2316,2466,"that you slipped her a Vicodin?"],[2529,2666,"I know you used to take that shit"],[2666,2741,"to go to sleep."],[2879,3016,"Your word against mine."],[3041,3254,"We could make this all go away"],[3300,3404,"if you help me out."],[3441,3566,"Write me a little check"],[3566,3729,"and I'll delete the video."],[3775,3904,"How's 50 million sound?"],[3966,4091,"You know if I do this,"],[4166,4254,"it's never going to end."],[4254,4329,"You're just gonna keep asking"],[4329,4400,"for more."],[4450,4529,"Maybe."],[4554,4641,"Maybe not."],[4654,4754,"But who's to say?"],[4791,4979,"Oh, come on, Mason."],[5000,5079,"50 million?"],[5125,5304,"You wouldn't even notice it's gone"],[5304,5441,"when you have billions."],[5816,5891,"Mason?"]],"55":[[337,462,"What is she talking about?"],[541,891,"Oh, I'm talking about the fact that"],[891,1166,"your new hubby here is a billionaire."],[1200,1391,"Something in which it seems"],[1391,1616,"he forgot to tell his new wife."],[1662,1741,"You're lying."],[1925,2054,"Tell me she's lying."],[2100,2229,"You're a construction worker, right?"],[2312,2366,"Bailey, I-"],[2366,2691,"Oh, you are even dumber"],[2691,2791,"than you look."],[2825,2954,"How could you be married"],[2954,3141,"to the CEO of Apex"],[3141,3316,"and not even fucking know it?"],[3337,3416,"CEO?"],[3529,3604,"Mason..."],[3679,3904,"Bailey, I can explain."],[3941,4000,"Explain to me"],[4000,4125,"that you've been lying to me"],[4125,4254,"since the moment I met you?"],[4754,4825,"Bailey."],[4866,4941,"Bailey, wait."],[5054,5279,"Seems like you lost your live-in maid."],[5387,5462,"Shame."],[5733,5812,"Fuck."]],"56":[[670,825,"Bailey, please."],[987,1050,"Bailey."],[1191,1291,"Just talk to me."],[1329,1375,"Scream at me."],[1375,1416,"Hit me."],[1416,1566,"Just don't walk away like this."],[1604,1704,"I trusted you."],[1775,1875,"You lied to me."],[1879,2087,"Look, I never meant to hurt you."],[2154,2241,"But you did."],[2441,2612,"You hurt me worse than anyone."],[2716,2862,"I let you in."],[2916,3075,"I thought you were different."],[3237,3391,"Tell me, Mason."],[3462,3579,"Were you just using me"],[3579,3712,"to get custody of Hannah?"],[3729,3850,"And once you got her,"],[3850,4025,"were you just going to throw me away"],[4025,4112,"like I was nothing?"],[4112,4225,"Of course not."],[4391,4554,"You made Hannah happy."],[4662,4829,"And you made me whole again."],[4925,5041,"How could I trust you?"],[5079,5241,"You made Hannah lie to me."],[5387,5612,"You played me like everyone else."],[5612,5729,"No, it was real for me."],[5779,5962,"Every fucking second was the most real"],[5962,6104,"that my life has ever been."],[7237,7425,"The idea of you being a billionaire"],[7425,7566,"scares the hell out of me."],[7666,7766,"But your lies?"],[8554,8641,"I can't be with someone"],[8641,8729,"I can't trust."],[8850,8937,"I'm sorry."]],"57":[[395,483,"Where are you going?"],[483,633,"You lost the right to know that."],[770,925,"Bailey, Bailey, please."],[937,1050,"I have to get to work."],[1070,1150,"What if you didn't have to"],[1150,1237,"work anymore?"],[1537,1662,"What exactly does that mean?"],[2100,2245,"I can take care of you, Bailey."],[2400,2487,"I'm a billionaire."],[2487,2612,"Let me give you the world."],[5158,5383,"I had the whole world."],[6670,6858,"If you just said, I'm scared too,"],[6958,7050,"I would have stayed."]],"58":[[354,533,"What are you doing in here?"],[691,916,"Now the drunk sub is homeless too."],[970,1058,"Please, sir."],[1079,1208,"I had nowhere else to go."],[1258,1358,"Did your husband kick you out"],[1358,1491,"once he learned you were drunk?"],[1491,1604,"I'm not a drunk."],[1670,1845,"Clarice Cain set me up."],[1920,2133,"But I was wrong about him."],[2233,2404,"He wasn't the man he said he was."],[2458,2554,"Well, young lady,"],[2554,2716,"I am legally obligated"],[2716,2845,"to file a report on this."],[2866,3079,"I really need this job."],[3229,3320,"Okay, fine."],[3341,3508,"You can have your old janitor job back."],[3508,3608,"But you can forget about"],[3608,3695,"ever teaching again."],[3695,3820,"Do I make myself clear?"],[3820,3891,"Clear."],[3945,4091,"Thank you, Principal Davis."],[4120,4270,"No more sob stories."],[4329,4495,"Let's give her something to clean."],[5120,5220,"Stop it."]],"59":[[20,125,"Stop it."],[262,345,"Ew!"],[345,562,"Now Hannah has janitor germs."],[562,645,"Let's get out of here"],[645,775,"before we get them too."],[1233,1370,"Now you're the one saving me."],[1437,1662,"Why didn't you come with us?"],[1800,1912,"I wanted to, baby."],[1912,1962,"It's,"],[2025,2133,"it's complicated."],[2150,2300,"So you don't like Daddy?"],[2345,2412,"I do."],[2462,2633,"More than I ever thought possible."],[2770,2887,"That's what makes this so hard."]],"60":[[733,804,"Hey, Banana."],[804,870,"How was school?"],[895,1029,"I just wanted Mommy"],[1029,1183,"to come with us."],[1208,1308,"Look, I know."],[1483,1545,"I'm sorry."],[1608,1795,"Don't apologize to me."],[1795,1945,"Apologize to Mommy."],[1966,2104,"She's really sad."],[2104,2216,"I tried, Banana."],[2283,2454,"She doesn't want to talk to me anymore."],[2479,2645,"Then try harder."],[2666,2904,"You're clearly not good at it."],[3045,3170,"You're savage, you know that?"],[3208,3433,"You're the one who made Mommy cry."],[3433,3570,"So go fix it."],[3633,3783,"You're absolutely right, Banana."],[3920,3970,"Hey, Smith."],[3970,4054,"Stay here with Hannah."],[4054,4120,"I'll be right back."],[4183,4333,"I'm gonna go find Mommy, okay?"],[4545,4720,"Bring her home, Daddy."],[4729,4783,"Okay."]],"61":[[829,904,"Hey, sis."],[987,1112,"What do you want, Danny?"],[1220,1329,"I'm gonna take you home."],[1416,1475,"I'd rather go live"],[1475,1591,"in the janitor's closet"],[1591,1729,"than go back with you and Vanessa."],[1787,1879,"You shut the fuck up."],[1879,1937,"Get in the car."],[1937,1979,"Come on."],[2083,2154,"Get in the car."],[2154,2204,"Come on!"],[2225,2275,"Shut-"],[2279,2404,"Get your hands off her!"],[2466,2537,"Get in!"],[3425,3504,"Smith, bring the car"],[3504,3587,"around the alley real quick."],[3587,3662,"They took Bailey."]],"62":[[187,275,"I have the package."],[312,387,"Yeah, we're right outside"],[387,445,"the building."],[483,600,"Yes, yes, sir."],[600,675,"Yeah, thank you."],[712,775,"Thank you."],[787,837,"Thank you."],[920,1012,"Let me go!"],[1037,1137,"You're sick!"],[1137,1333,"Selling your own sister like this!"],[1333,1583,"They're going to kill me!"],[1637,1750,"Do you understand me, Bailey?"],[1820,2012,"If I don't pay this loan back today,"],[2012,2150,"they're going to come to my house"],[2150,2295,"and they're going to fucking kill me."],[2325,2408,"I don't care."],[2425,2575,"You're no family of mine!"],[2833,3025,"You're gonna sleep with Mr. Pitt."],[3087,3225,"I'm gonna get my 30k,"],[3225,3287,"and then this"],[3420,3508,"is all just gonna be"],[3508,3570,"a bad dream."],[3629,3700,"Okay?"],[3975,4058,"Let me go!"],[4108,4250,"Danny, stop them!"]],"63":[[654,712,"Alright."],[779,875,"Alright!"],[937,1079,"I got your fucking money."],[2162,2229,"Where is she?"],[2229,2325,"You motherfucker,"],[2325,2454,"you broke my nose!"],[2454,2566,"Wrong answer."],[3254,3325,"Come on, man."],[3350,3450,"I'm your brother-in-law."],[3475,3600,"This is how you treat family?"],[3600,3800,"You have no right to talk about family."],[3816,3979,"Tell me where Bailey is."],[3979,4050,"Now!"],[4058,4154,"Fuck you!"],[4629,4704,"Wait!"],[4725,4900,"You're not breaking that vase!"],[4966,5095,"She's at Mr. Pitt's."],[5133,5241,"He's giving Danny 30k"],[5241,5316,"to sleep with her."],[5316,5408,"Vanessa!"],[5716,5812,"It was either the vase"],[5812,5925,"or your husband's face."],[6004,6141,"You're lucky I'm feeling merciful."],[6283,6462,"You stupid construction worker!"],[6470,6575,"That vase was worth"],[6575,6716,"more than your entire life!"]],"64":[[925,1075,"Still struggling, I see, huh?"],[1137,1220,"I don't get it."],[1295,1412,"A lot of women would kill"],[1437,1570,"to be in your situation."],[1625,1825,"Living a life of luxury."],[1875,2050,"A real fox in the sheets."],[2133,2200,"Like me,"],[2262,2450,"I'm the total package, babe."],[2600,2783,"Don't touch me."],[2875,2933,"Look."],[3008,3137,"I own you now, doll."],[3250,3408,"You need to face the facts"],[3475,3612,"and stop fighting it."]],"65":[[41,195,"You need to face the facts"],[270,395,"and stop fighting it."],[633,904,"I'm getting so sick and tired"],[904,1008,"of your shit!"],[1183,1245,"Bitch!"],[1341,1566,"Mr. Cain of Apex Building Group"],[1566,1666,"is here to see you."],[1666,1791,"He says it's urgent."],[2033,2133,"Must be important."],[2233,2329,"You know I'm his"],[2329,2470,"number one iron supplier?"],[2516,2595,"Yeah, me."],[2883,2958,"Send him in."],[3183,3245,"You know what?"],[3291,3420,"This could work out fine."],[3441,3570,"Never met him in person."],[3645,3779,"You, me, him?"],[3820,3945,"Could have a little fun, huh?"],[3983,4095,"Get things spicy?"],[4266,4470,"I hear he's very, very handsome."],[4833,5045,"Step away from my wife."]],"66":[[179,391,"Step away from my wife."],[470,533,"You?"],[683,866,"You're that lowlife construction boy."],[920,1070,"How the fuck did you get in here?"],[1070,1183,"I'm Mason Cain,"],[1258,1470,"owner of Apex Building Group."],[1470,1529,"Yeah."],[1541,1600,"Right."],[1904,2020,"You let her go."],[2045,2129,"Now."],[2208,2266,"Uh-uh."],[2358,2558,"I paid for her fair and square."],[2620,2745,"She belongs to me now,"],[2745,2945,"so get the fuck out of here."],[3008,3070,"Mason."],[3133,3270,"Think about Hannah."],[3308,3420,"I'm not leaving you."],[3720,3883,"You say you bought her fair and square?"],[3970,4020,"Yeah."],[4045,4179,"Like a business transaction."],[4304,4366,"Well then."],[4500,4658,"Let me put this in business terms."],[4987,5191,"You just lost your contract with Apex."]],"67":[[91,283,"You just lost your contract with Apex."],[458,550,"Woah woah, woah!"],[550,604,"Oh,"],[604,762,"be very, very careful."],[816,962,"You think you can scare me"],[962,1050,"with your lies?"],[1066,1187,"You know who you're talking to?"],[1204,1504,"I'm Nathanial fucking Pitt."],[1529,1591,"Who are you?"],[1616,1750,"Nothing but a laborer."],[1775,2050,"Born poor, you're gonna die poor."],[2154,2204,"Sir!"],[2204,2287,"What now?"],[2329,2462,"We just lost Apex."],[2487,2654,"They severed all ties with us."],[2675,2754,"That's impossible."],[2754,2891,"Get the fuck out of here!"],[2962,3091,"You fucking bastard."],[3425,3504,"Bastard!"],[3650,3804,"If I don't have Apex's contract,"],[3904,4016,"I'm fucking nothing."],[4416,4541,"Who the fuck are you?"],[4716,4887,"I told you who I was, asshole."],[4979,5112,"You're just too stupid to realize"],[5112,5250,"you messed with the wrong woman."],[5500,5775,"Alright boys, he's all yours."],[5841,5941,"Nathanial Pitt."],[6041,6175,"You're under arrest."],[6304,6391,"Kidnapping."],[6525,6579,"Assault."],[6583,6704,"Attempted rape."],[6737,6841,"Get your hands off me."],[6900,6962,"Now!"]],"68":[[25,141,"Get your hands off me."],[212,379,"Thanks for the tip, Mr. Cain."],[450,525,"Mr. Cain,"],[566,737,"this is all a big misunderstanding."],[766,841,"Look, look."],[841,991,"We can negotiate something."],[1016,1191,"I'll cut you a real good deal, I promise."],[1216,1312,"Mr. Cain!"],[1616,1691,"Did he hurt you?"],[1762,1816,"No."],[1904,2029,"You got here just in time."],[2266,2379,"I got someone"],[2454,2579,"waiting for you in the car"],[2579,2679,"if you want to say hi."],[3516,3729,"Mommy, you're alright!"],[3762,3991,"I'm so happy to see you, baby girl."],[4029,4304,"I don't want you to sleep in the closet."],[4329,4604,"Daddy, can Mommy come with us?"],[4791,4862,"Closet?"],[5079,5250,"I didn't have anywhere else to go."],[5362,5437,"I'm fine, Hannah."],[5479,5541,"It's okay."],[5591,5687,"Bailey, will you please"],[5687,5787,"just stay with us?"],[5850,6012,"At least until Hannah's birthday."]],"69":[[50,187,"Just, just please stay with us,"],[187,325,"at least until Hannah's birthday."],[500,670,"Just until I figure out where I'm going."],[670,720,"Yay!"],[720,962,"Mommy is coming home with us!"],[2937,3008,"Oh, my."],[3850,3925,"Welcome home."],[4012,4112,"Come on, Mommy."],[4112,4250,"Let me give you a tour."],[4620,4750,"Good evening, Mrs. Cain."],[4762,4883,"It's nice to finally meet you."],[4900,4987,"Anything you need,"],[4987,5150,"you just let Mrs. Flannigan know."],[5225,5312,"Come on."],[5958,6008,"Would you please"],[6008,6162,"make Mrs. Cain some dinner?"],[6208,6337,"She's had a long day."],[6400,6487,"Right away, sir."],[6700,6758,"Thank you."],[6925,7037,"Bailey, you're my wife."],[7133,7237,"Let me take care of you."]],"70":[[554,654,"You can take the master."],[654,854,"I'll sleep in one of the guest bedrooms."],[979,1129,"I don't want to turn you out, Mason."],[1216,1329,"I want you in my bed."],[1716,1841,"This place is unreal."],[2104,2279,"It's all meaningless without you."],[2954,3029,"It's just..."],[3262,3391,"I don't know if I can trust you yet."],[3629,3775,"Let's just get through Hannah's birthday."],[3908,3983,"Okay."],[4454,4529,"Good night."]],"71":[[395,537,"Mommy, wake up!"],[608,833,"Daddy and I have a surprise for you."],[875,937,"What? - Come on."],[1300,1433,"Don't peek."],[1450,1587,"We're almost there."],[1587,1745,"Hannah, I'm going to trip."],[1845,2008,"Open your eyes."],[3033,3170,"Hannah, what is all this?"],[3233,3550,"We got all of these gifts from SHEIN."],[3658,3870,"Banana was the Creative Director."],[3925,4262,"Look, this one's from SHEIN MOTF!"],[4283,4512,"It's like movie-star fancy."],[4587,4875,"And this one's MASURA SHEIN."],[4908,5008,"And it makes you"],[5008,5270,"look like a total girl boss."],[5337,5700,"And also, this one's from SHEIN BAE."],[5700,5887,"This is my favorite."],[5912,6187,"You'll look like a total Princess in it."],[6337,6525,"Do you like all my gifts?"],[6537,6633,"Of course."],[6687,6812,"You're my favorite gift."],[6870,7045,"Group hug time."]],"72":[[1187,1250,"To Hannah."],[1275,1350,"To Hannah."],[1787,1995,"It's so easy for rich kids to get spoiled."],[2020,2175,"But Hannah's different."],[2245,2337,"She has a heart of gold."],[2350,2520,"I didn't grow up rich, Bailey."],[2579,2762,"Everything I have, I made myself."],[2820,3008,"I taught Hannah not to be entitled"],[3008,3162,"just because her dad has money."],[3212,3308,"I bet you thought I was some"],[3308,3450,"rich private school kid, huh?"],[3512,3612,"Well, yeah."],[3675,3750,"Actually."],[3812,4000,"Look, I know what it feels like"],[4000,4120,"to be deceived, Bailey."],[4170,4287,"A lot of women have tried"],[4287,4370,"to come into my life"],[4370,4450,"for the wrong reasons."],[4450,4637,"And I've always tried to protect Hannah"],[4637,4725,"from that kind of hurt."],[5045,5133,"Fuck no."]],"73":[[283,375,"Fuck no."],[795,845,"Come on."],[845,900,"You're coming."],[995,1095,"What the hell do you think"],[1095,1175,"you're doing here?"],[1233,1358,"I have a court order"],[1400,1595,"granting me visitation rights."],[1633,1758,"I'm taking Hannah."],[1775,1875,"Hannah, let's go."],[1900,1987,"No, no."],[1987,2162,"I don't want to go with you."],[2208,2395,"You better keep your hands off of me,"],[2425,2537,"or I will tell the judge"],[2537,2708,"that you roughed me up."],[2708,2845,"You have no right to take Hannah."],[2845,2962,"I have a restraining order."],[3058,3212,"Not anymore, you don't."],[3258,3425,"You see, the judge found out"],[3425,3712,"about your wife's little drunk mishap."],[3737,3858,"And rescinded it."],[3975,4187,"Daddy, don't let her take me."],[4187,4358,"Stop crying."],[4425,4570,"You're coming with me."],[4587,4700,"And you're gonna like it."],[4750,5000,"Over my dead body."]],"74":[[170,225,"It's okay."],[225,312,"I won't let her take you."],[462,662,"You drugged me, Clarice."],[712,937,"And I will be pressing charges."],[987,1162,"And if you think for a second"],[1162,1237,"that I'll let you leave"],[1237,1320,"with my child,"],[1375,1487,"you're more delusional"],[1487,1558,"than I thought."],[1558,1737,"You're not her mother,"],[1787,2000,"you infertile bitch."],[2225,2425,"I might not be her mother biologically,"],[2475,2570,"but I love her."],[2625,2770,"And I won't stand by"],[2770,2920,"while a psycho like you"],[2920,3062,"puts her hands on my daughter."],[3212,3287,"Well then."],[3350,3537,"I guess I'll see you both in court"],[3537,3625,"next week."],[3662,3837,"And we'll settle all of this then."],[4337,4433,"Whoops."],[4550,4712,"Happy birthday, Hannah."]],"75":[[41,262,"Don't let her take me, Mommy."],[275,416,"I won't, baby girl."],[454,562,"She may have papers,"],[562,666,"but you know what we got?"],[687,766,"The truth."],[812,975,"She won't get away with this."],[1066,1154,"And your daddy?"],[1241,1379,"He would move heaven and earth"],[1379,1529,"before he let her get you again."],[1562,1675,"She's right, Banana."],[1704,1891,"I'll never stop fighting for you."],[2191,2275,"We'll be in the other room"],[2275,2379,"if you need anything, okay?"],[2412,2487,"Okay."],[2554,2604,"Alright."],[3591,3754,"Look, I'm sorry for all the drama."],[3754,3929,"I know you didn't sign up for this."],[4000,4162,"I don't blame you, Mason."],[4275,4329,"I just don't know"],[4329,4429,"how a mother could do that"],[4429,4562,"on her daughter's birthday."],[4650,4787,"You know, we'll make it up to Hannah."],[4816,4941,"Her birthday is actually Monday,"],[4941,5066,"so we can make a day of it."],[5229,5291,"Wait."],[5441,5625,"Monday is October 15th."],[5754,5904,"Mason, is Hannah's birthday"],[5904,6112,"October 15th, 2019?"],[6166,6229,"Yeah."],[6466,6575,"Bailey, what's wrong?"],[6704,6850,"Mason, is Hannah"],[6850,6975,"your biological daughter?"]],"76":[[58,187,"Mason, is Hannah"],[187,333,"your biological daughter?"],[450,600,"Yeah, of course she is."],[800,875,"I'm sorry."],[945,1037,"For a second, I thought-"],[1037,1262,"But Clarice isn't her biological mother."],[1350,1500,"We used an egg donor."],[1712,1783,"Could it be?"],[1845,1970,"Has fate led me here?"],[2133,2275,"When my eggs were stolen,"],[2291,2462,"the police found the fertility clinic."],[2525,2700,"All the records had been destroyed."],[3037,3175,"They managed to recover this."],[3687,3820,"Don't move, I'm gonna be right back."],[3937,4000,"Mason."]],"77":[[1912,1987,"Open it."],[2662,2900,"Clarice never wanted to carry a baby,"],[2900,3012,"so we used a surrogate"],[3012,3100,"and an egg donor."],[3287,3470,"Hannah is my daughter."],[3500,3633,"She's our daughter."],[3670,3775,"Our Hannah."],[3800,3875,"Oh my-"],[4275,4362,"I found you."],[4475,4600,"How did I find you?"],[4745,4870,"We found each other."]],"78":[[295,458,"You'll never be lost again, Bailey."],[654,708,"Wait."],[733,891,"Bailey, my God, I just remembered."],[891,991,"I wanted Hannah to be able to"],[991,1091,"have full siblings one day."],[1091,1245,"I still have all the fertilized eggs."],[1275,1316,"Mason-"],[1316,1491,"They were cryogenically frozen."],[1545,1795,"I'm saying, you can have more kids."],[1795,1945,"We can have more kids."],[2033,2129,"I never thought I would have"],[2129,2233,"one child."],[2366,2483,"This is a dream."],[2529,2633,"It's a miracle."],[2808,2958,"Mommy, Daddy!"],[2995,3058,"Hannah!"],[3104,3195,"Baby, you were right."],[3195,3329,"Bailey is your mommy."],[3329,3458,"Your real mommy."],[3479,3537,"Duh!"],[3537,3683,"I've always known."],[3883,4070,"Clarice doesn't stand a chance."],[4083,4300,"I will fight for everything"],[4300,4458,"that belongs to me."]],"79":[[45,233,"For letting the lonely janitor think"],[233,383,"she's good enough to teach at my school."],[416,516,"God's sake."],[554,654,"I bet a drunk like you"],[654,816,"doesn't even have a teaching license."],[841,958,"No, I do."],[958,1095,"I want to be a teacher."],[1095,1195,"That's not happening."],[1195,1291,"Not at this school."],[1333,1416,"Put yourself together."],[1416,1487,"The kids are watching you."],[1487,1508,"God-"],[1641,1783,"Furthermore, your honor,"],[1820,2095,"my client served as a loving mother"],[2095,2283,"to Hannah Cain for three years"],[2283,2408,"before the divorce."],[2483,2766,"Bailey is nothing but a homewrecker"],[2766,2866,"and a drunk."],[2883,2995,"I can't understand"],[2995,3145,"how any parent would be alright"],[3145,3245,"with this person"],[3245,3358,"caring for their child."],[3429,3658,"Counsel, begin your direct examination."],[3658,3733,"I'd love to see"],[3733,3895,"what excuse your client has."]],"80":[[33,108,"Mr. Cain."],[195,295,"Who is that woman?"],[445,633,"She is the biological mother"],[633,783,"of my daughter Hannah Cain"],[883,958,"and my wife."],[1120,1208,"Excuse me?"],[1320,1508,"Bailey is Hannah's mother."],[1558,1695,"What is this bullshit?"],[1733,1816,"Your honor,"],[1895,2170,"we have DNA evidence to prove it."],[2445,2608,"How is this possible?"],[2679,2791,"Clarice lied to me"],[2870,3070,"and bought eggs off the black market"],[3070,3158,"for our surrogate."],[3245,3445,"Bailey's eggs were stolen from her"],[3445,3554,"when she was a minor."],[3941,4158,"You dealt in the black market?"],[4333,4529,"I just needed a child."],[4558,4733,"She also drugged Bailey at work."]],"81":[[41,220,"She also drugged Bailey at work."],[483,566,"We have witnesses"],[566,708,"who saw her at the elementary school"],[708,766,"that day."],[1383,1520,"Do you two love each other?"],[1987,2129,"We do, your honor."],[2283,2441,"And you plan on staying married?"],[2541,2683,"Yes, your honor."],[2829,2954,"Then there's no better place"],[2954,3045,"for Hannah to be."],[3083,3266,"I grant full custody"],[3266,3408,"to Mrs. And Mr. Cain"],[3408,3558,"of their biological daughter."],[6429,6645,"Mommy, Daddy, you did it!"],[6645,6708,"Come here."],[6908,6983,"Hey, Banana,"],[6983,7033,"how would you like"],[7033,7166,"a little brother or sister?"],[7183,7320,"One of each, please."],[7408,7512,"Sounds perfect to me."]]}